pageProduct.name: Aussie Bodies Lo Carb Whipped Chocolate 50g
pageProduct.description:
General Information

14g PROTEIN
0.4g SUGARS
HIGH FIBRE
No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Our Pro-active Nutrition products help your shape body from the inside out. Since 1991

Product Claims: 14g PROTEIN, 0.4g SUGARS , HIGH FIBRE, No artificial colours, flavours or preservatives.

Size: 50g

Flavour: Whipped Chocolate

Serving Size: 50g

Servings Per Pack: 1

KEY FEATURES

• Proactive Nutrition
• Great Tasting
• Guilt-Free Indulgence
• Source of Protein

Warnings

"Contains: Milk, Soy and Peanuts.
May Contain: Cereals Containing Gluten (Wheat, Oats), Tree Nuts (Almonds, Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.
"

CAUTION

Excess consumption may have a laxative effect.

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Aussie Bodies® Protein Blend (30%) [Calcium Caseinate (Milk), Whey Protein Isolate (Milk), Soy Protein Isolate, Soy Protein Crisps (Soy Protein Isolate, Cocoa Powder, Tapioca Starch), Emulsifiers (Soy Lecithin, Mono- and Di-glycerides of Fatty Acids)], Sweetener (Polydextrose), No Added Sugar Dark Chocolate (18%) (Cocoa Mass, Cocoa Butter, Sweeteners (Polydextrose, Erythritol, Steviol Glycosides), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Natural Flavour), Sweetener (Sorbitol), Humectant (Glycerol), No Added Sugar Milk Chocolate Chips (4.5%) (Sweeteners (Polydextrose, Erythritol, Monk Fruit Extract, Steviol Glycosides), Cocoa Butter, Milk Solids, Cocoa Mass, Inulin, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Natural Flavour), Cocoa Powder, Vegetable Oil, Cocoa Mass, Natural Flavours, Salt, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin).

Contains: Contains: Milk and Soy.
May Contain: Cereals Containing Gluten (Wheat, Oats), Peanuts, Tree Nuts (Almonds, Hazelnuts) and Sesame Seeds.

Allergen Contains: Milk| Soy

Allergen May Be Present: Almonds| Hazelnuts| Oats| Peanuts| Sesame Seeds| Tree Nuts| Wheat| Cereals Containing Gluten

Directions

Store in a cool, dry place, below 30°C. Keep out of direct sunlight.
